  "Subtitle": {
    "English": "Freighter-Mounted Teleportation Device",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "货船内置传送装置",
    "TraditionalChinese": "配備於貨船的瞬間傳送裝置"
  },
  "Description": {
    "English": "A device that modulates standard freighter communication signals to enable the <span class=\"name name-technology\">interplanetary transport of matter</span> as well as data.<br><br>Freighters fitted with such a device can send and receive products and substances to a user's <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Exosuit</span> over a <span class=\"name name-stellar\">long distance</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一种用来调节标准货船通讯信号的装置，使之能够<span class=\"name name-technology\">跨星际传输物质</span>和数据。<br><br>安装了此设备的货船能够跨越<span class=\"name name-stellar\">长距离</span>向使用者的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">套装</span>发送或接收产品和物质。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "將標準貨船傳通訊訊號模組化、以啟用<span class=\"name name-technology\">跨星球物質傳輸裝置</span>及資料傳輸。<br><br>配備了這種裝置的貨船可以<span class=\"name name-stellar\">遠端</span>傳送並接收使用者<span class=\"name name-stellar\">強化套裝</span>的產品與物質。"
  },
